description: Given a date (today, Saturday, July 1st, etc...), the Daily Food skill will tell you which food and/or drinks are celebrated on that day.   Great conversation starters, and this skill may even help you decide what to cook for dinner each week!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Daily Food for Saturday
Alexa, get food for today from Daily Food
Alexa, open Daily Food and get food for tomorrow.
name: Daily Food
shortDescription: Daily Food keeps you informed on national food/drinks celebrated throughout the year in the United States.
